 the visible light from the Sun to pass through and reach Earth&rsquo;s surface. As Earth&rsquo;s surface is heated by sunlight, it radiates part of this energy back toward space as infrared radiation. This radiation, unlike visible light, tends to be absorbed by the greenhouse gases in the atmosphere, raising its temperature. The heated atmosphere in turn radiates infrared radiation back toward Earth&rsquo;s surface. <br />\n<br />\n如果將陽光直接反射就無問題"},{"pid":"39920262d0b89892eb4c91aabcd1c662098da80c","tid":2493475,"uid":36544,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOofsoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOofsoC.jpg&h=b7fa4f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n矛盾大對決"},{"pid":"512f572037a82cfebeb22545b9a736652b1e60fc","tid":2493475,"uid":352873,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"超白漆普通話點讀?"},{"pid":"cfeb54eb41f6608da96485c4ee73479dec41769a","tid":2493475,"uid":1544,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"512f572037a82cfebeb22545b9a736652b1e60fc","tid":2493475,"uid":352873,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"超白漆普通話點讀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"超北七"},{"pid":"60e65550db998c7108380c16793ea73c018b4d6b","tid":2493475,"uid":14918,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:29:14.000Z","msg":"反射咁多上太空<br />\n會唔會引起外星人不滿"},{"pid":"739948006f0c5c28beb1e2b995dc7e6d5a820a72","tid":2493475,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"超白漆防塵？"},{"pid":"db8029c89ab4ab7036ab8ca5d987bc1c0ae49b8e","tid":2493475,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"全地面使用解決全球暖化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1adbfc30a4773309c4a400ccb27c595dbfd5ba",